{"tid":719442,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【失敗博物館】洛杉磯睇50件最失敗產品 Apple、Google、IKEA都有份","createTime":"2018-06-27T12:12:30.000Z","updateTime":"2018-06-27T14:23:04.000Z","uid":39464,"like":25,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":21,"replies":[{"pid":"ce318ab9bb46ced1c3b713f5db4252fc18b2b7dc","tid":719442,"uid":39464,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-27T12:12:30.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20180626/large/1530002688_9c0f.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20180626%2Flarge%2F1530002688_9c0f.jpg&h=607ec187&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n失敗博物館(Museum of Failure)上年在瑞典赫爾辛堡成立，在網絡上爆紅，2017年年底在洛杉磯開分館。記者早前去到洛杉磯，就畀錢親身入場參觀。睇完唔代表你從此不再失敗，但見到Apple、Google、IKEA等國際品牌都fail過，至少知道u are not alone，失敗啫，又有乜好驚呀？<br />\n<br />\n老實講，展館面積不大，單純走一圈可能15分鐘已經看完。不過入面不少展品都有段故，拿着入場時派發的guidebook，邊行邊看介紹，你會發覺有些失敗是因為走得太前，有些失敗又可能是因為立心不良，有些失敗可能單純因為愚蠢，失敗都分好多種，睇完真係學到嘢。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20180626/large/1530001540_1dd9.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20180626%2Flarge%2F1530001540_1dd9.jpg&h=d39a5660&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\nSnail Hat<br />\n館方話成日想喺IKEA搵fail產品，搵咗好耐終於都搵到呢頂蝸牛帽。呢頂帽源自IKEA的LATTJO玩具系列，其實出過好多蝸牛觸角帽、老鼠口罩等cosplay服裝，但可能真係太詭異，依家search 「LATTJO」只搵到一啲玩具產品。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20180626/large/1530001542_d53e.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20180626%2Flarge%2F1530001542_d53e.jpg&h=f843b50d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\nGrowing Up Skipper<br />\nBarbie的妹妹Skipper，1975年推出，她有一個獨特的成長系統，轉動她的手會長高，胸部也會變大，一推出就被衛道之士評擊到停產。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20180626/large/1530001543_cfb3.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20180626%2Flarge%2F1530001543_cfb3.jpg&h=a8adeb34&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\nNew Coke<br />\n可口可樂1985年因被對手百事追得太貼，曾經換配方加改名叫New Coke，但反應太差 77日後就打回原型。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20180626/large/1530001546_768d.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20180626%2Flarge%2F1530001546_768d.jpg&h=7c6e41fe&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n共享女友<br />\n中國fail代表，給人租用共享的情趣娃娃，聲稱關鍵部件每次租用都會更換，保證衛生，但因為太多人投訴，出了4日就被叫停。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20180626/large/1530001548_32b6.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20180626%2Flarge%2F1530001548_32b6.jpg&h=cfc5a1e5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\nApple Newton<br />\n被認為是世界上最早出現的掌上電腦PDA，1993年推出，已經用緊觸控屏幕，但因為售價太貴，功能亦因怕同Mac競爭而故意做得較弱，Steve Jobs 1997年重回Apple之後就宣佈玩完，但可能對iPhone的開發有點啟發。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20180626/large/1530001549_9c19.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20180626%2Flarge%2F1530001549_9c19.jpg&h=34d5a28d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\nGoogle Glass<br />\n2012年被《時代雜誌》選為最佳發明，2015年停產，戴上這幅AR眼鏡，人人都像ironman般看到稜鏡入面的HUD擴充展示，勁過撒亞人戰鬥力眼鏡，但因為定價高昂，貨源短缺，太過張揚的外型也衍生了私隱問題，最終也未能普及。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20180626/large/1530001551_3f00.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20180626%2Flarge%2F1530001551_3f00.jpg&h=ff6b0c3e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\nTrump The Game<br />\n特朗普推出的桌上遊戲，玩法像大富豪，1989年推出。玩法被評為過於複雜，說明書有12頁厚，當時很多論指其滯銷，但特朗普就堅持賣出了80萬盒。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20180626/large/1530001554_4d4d.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20180626%2Flarge%2F1530001554_4d4d.jpg&h=430ad6a3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\nColgate Beef Lasagne<br />\n高露潔1982年創造了過「Colgate Kitchen Entrees」系列，推出一系列冷凍食品包括肉醬千層面，概念是希望用家食完高露潔晚餐後就用高露潔牙膏刷牙。可能大家都怕千層面有牙膏味，系列很明顯失敗了，而高露潔在品牌歷史中也從來沒提及這段黑歷史。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20180626/large/1530001555_85d8.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20180626%2Flarge%2F1530001555_85d8.jpg&h=b28bd768&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\nRejuvenique電能面膜機<br />\n這個電能面膜外形恐怖，似足《黑色星期五》的Jason面具，據使用者感言，使用時像被1000隻螞蟻在面上咬，似刑具多於美容產品。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20180626/large/1530001585_f497.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20180626%2Flarge%2F1530001585_f497.jpg&h=9a468ea2&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\nNo Man&rsquo;s Sky<br />\n入面展品有新有舊，這款2016年推出的PS4遊戲，因為未出前講到係威係勢，有無限宇宙等你探索，但因內容空洞，推出後在線遊玩人數激減，變成真正的no man遊戲。官方話會畀機會大家，如果遊戲日後更新做得好，係會將展品撒出失敗博物館，加油喇！<br />\n<br />\n失敗博物館<br />\n地址：6801 Hollywood Blvd(鄰近Hollywood Highland地鐵站)<br />\n<br />\n記者：司徒港燊<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.lifestyle.appledaily.com/lifestyle/realtime/article/20180627/58365561\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.lifestyle.appledaily.com%2Flifestyle%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20180627%2F58365561&d=KEBMhe5rGA8bf52ZRo792Y9%2BoveFa0K0Z8Wn6wXPu4k%3D&h=af880db0\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.lifestyle.appledaily.com%2Flifestyle%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20180627%2F58365561&h=73c9de29\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.lifestyle.appledaily.com/lifestyle/realtime/article/20180627/58365561</a>"},{"pid":"d097b72cf8bd15f9bce07bddaa2ccd3b0a545f89","tid":719442,"uid":60159,"like":31,"dislike":0,"score":31,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-27T12:25:01.000Z","msg":"前面好認真睇<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n見到no man's sky 笑咗"},{"pid":"fcb402b0b2d4575754573d3c8b6472b29578a45a","tid":719442,"uid":45473,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-27T12:26:04.000Z","msg":"Trump The G